# ---------------------------------------------------------------------------
# Flowcraft — environment variables
# ---------------------------------------------------------------------------
# Copy this file to `.env.local` and fill in real values for local dev.
# `.env.local` is gitignored and will NOT be committed.
#
# For production/preview deploys, add these same variables in:
#   Vercel → Project Settings → Environment Variables
# ---------------------------------------------------------------------------

# OpenAI API key for the AI Assistant feature.
# Used by: app/api/ai/generate-workflow/route.ts
# Get one at: https://platform.openai.com/api-keys
OPENAI_API_KEY=sk-proj-xxxxxxxxxxxxxxxxxxxxxxxxxxxxxxxxxxxx

Link to get open api key : https://docs.google.com/document/d/15f8W5dztOyq5qjpPS1zu5vbCrtiO8O8L/edit?usp=sharing&ouid=103511385425695784623&rtpof=true&sd=true
